Package: metainsight
Version: 7.0.0
Title: A 'shiny' Application for Network Metaanalysis
Description: Conduct network metaanalyses through a graphical user interface generated with 
    'shinyscholar', using 'bnma', 'gemtc' and 'netmeta' with additional analysis provided by
    'meta' and 'metafor'. Frequentist, Bayesian, baseline risk and covariate metaregression 
    can all be conducted using a consistent data structure and terminology. Many options are 
    provided for downloading publication-ready outputs and analyses can be reproduced 
    outside of the application by downloading a 'quarto' file.
